text: Don Ruben Ecleo, formerly Baltazar, is one of 12 Barangays of the municipality of San Jose, Dinagat Islands, Philippines. The barangay is north of the town proper of San Jose, in the Southern portion of the province.Don Ruben Ecleo (Baltazar), Dinagat Islands - Google Maps == References == == External links == * Province of Dinagat Islands - Official webpage Category:Philippines geography stubs Category:Barangays of Dinagat Islands
